#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:25
msgid ""
"The origin of an object is shown in the 3D View by a small orange circle. This is highlighted in "
"the image to the right by the red arrow. It tells Blender the relative position of that object in "
"3D space. What you see in the 3D View (vertices, edges, etc.) is what makes up the object."
msgstr ""
"在三维视图中一个物体的原心由一个小的橙色圆圈显示。这在红色箭头右侧的图像中高亮显示。它告诉Blender该"
"物体在3D空间中的相对位置。你在3D视图（顶点，边等）中看到的是构成物体的东西。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:30
msgid ""
"The origin does not have to be located in the center of the geometry (e.g. mesh). This means that "
"an object can have its origin located on one end of the mesh or even completely outside the mesh. "
"For example, the orange rectangle in the image has its origin located on the far left of the mesh."
msgstr ""
"原点不一定要位于几何体的中心（例如网格）。这意味着物体的原点可以位于网格的一端，甚至完全位于网格的外"
"部。例如，图像中的橙色矩形的原点位于网格的最左侧。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:35
msgid "Now let us examine: Rotation around the individual origins:"
msgstr "现在让我们来研究一下: 围绕各自的原心的旋转:"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:37
msgid ""
"The blue rectangle has its origin located in the center of the mesh, while the orange rectangle has "
"its origin located on the left-hand side."
msgstr "蓝色矩形的原点位于网格的中心，而橙色矩形的原点位于左侧。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:39
msgid ""
"When the Pivot Point is set to *Individual Origins*, the origin of each object (indicated by the "
"red arrow) remains in place while the object rotates around it in the path shown by the black arrow."
msgstr ""
"当轴心点被设置为 *各自的原心* 时，每个物体（由红色箭头指示）的原点保持原位，而物体在黑色箭头所示的路"
"径中围绕它旋转。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:45
msgid "Rotation around individual origins (middle) compared to the median point (right)."
msgstr "围绕各自的原心（中）和质心点（右）的旋转对比。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:49
msgid "Scaling around individual origins (middle) compared to the median point (right)."
msgstr "围绕各自的原心（中）和质心点（右）的缩放的对比。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:53
msgid "In Edit Mode"
msgstr "在编辑模式"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:55
msgid ""
"In Edit Mode, setting the Pivot Point to *Individual Origins* produces different results when the "
"selection mode is set to Vertex, Edge or Face. For example, Vertex mode produces results similar to "
"setting the pivot point to median and Edge mode often produces distorted results. Using Individual "
"Origins in Face mode produces the most predictable results."
msgstr ""
"在编辑模式中，将选择模式设置为顶点，边或面时，将轴心点设置为 *各自的原心* 会产生不同的结果。例如，顶"
"点模式产生的结果类似于将轴心点设置为质心点，而边模式经常产生扭曲的结果。在面模式中使用各自的原心产生"
"最可预测的结果。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:62
msgid "Rotation of individual faces around individual origins (middle) and the median point (right)."
msgstr "围绕各自的原心（中间）单独的面和围绕的质心点（右）旋转。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:67
msgid "Rotation of grouped faces with the pivot point indicated by the image text."
msgstr "用图像文本指示的轴心点旋转分组的面。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:69
msgid ""
"As can be seen in the images above, faces that touch each other will deform when rotated when the "
"pivot point is set to *Individual Origins*. Faces that do not touch will rotate around their "
"*Individual Origins* (their center)."
msgstr ""
"从上图中可以看出，当轴心点设置为 *各自的原心*  时，彼此接触的面将在旋转时变形。不接触的面将围绕它们"
"的 *各自的原心* （他们的中心）旋转。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:75
msgid ""
"Scaling with non-touching faces around individual origins (middle) and the median point (right)."
msgstr "围绕非接触面各自的原心（中间）和质心点（右侧）缩放。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:80
msgid "Scaling with touching faces."
msgstr "接触面缩放。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:82
msgid ""
"Groups of faces and F-gons can be scaled without their outside perimeter being deformed. However, "
"the individual faces inside will not be scaled uniformly."
msgstr "可以缩放一组面和多边形，而不会使外围变形。但是，内部的各个面不会被统一缩放。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:88
msgid "Modeling with faces and individual origins as the pivot point."
msgstr "用面和各自的原心为轴心点建模。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:90
msgid ""
"Once you are aware of its limitations and pitfalls, this tool can save a lot of time and lead to "
"unique shapes. This \"anemone\" was modeled from a 12 sided cylinder in about 10 minutes by "
"repeatedly using this workflow: Extrusions of individual faces, scaling with *median as a pivot "
"point*, and scaling and rotations of those faces with *Individual Origins as pivot points*."
msgstr ""
"一旦你意识到它的局限性和缺陷，这个工具可以节省大量的时间，并导致独特的形状。通过反复使用这个工作流"
"程，这个“海葵”从十二边的圆柱体中被创建出来：单个面的挤出，以 * 质心为轴心点的缩放*，以及以 *各自的原"
"心作为轴心点的缩放和旋转* 。"
